        "execSummary":  "Majorana 2 is a long-horizon platform bet, not a near-term enterprise tool ΓÇö but the embedded story is more immediately relevant: agentic AI was used to compress a multi-year R\u0026D cycle, demonstrating the operational leverage agents can deliver in knowledge-work domains. Enterprise leaders should note the pattern: AI agents running as autonomous research orchestrators accelerated a hard scientific problem. The same model ΓÇö agents handling high-volume, repetitive analytical work ΓÇö applies directly to customer operations, compliance review, and knowledge management. Microsoft\u0027s 2029 quantum timeline is speculative; treat this as a signal of platform ambition, not near-term deployment guidance.",
