        "execSummary":  "The 4.5x-10x velocity gains cited here are striking, but the article\u0027s more important insight is structural: high-performing teams are reorganizing work around AI agents, not just bolting AI onto existing processes. For technology and operations leaders, this implies that the competitive advantage from AI is process-design intelligence, not just tool access. Organizations that treat AI as a productivity add-on rather than a workflow redesign will likely see diminishing returns. Use this as a strategic framing document when building the business case for deeper AI operating model transformation.",
